           multiply  80                   by   w-cnt-stu-pnt-stu      .
           subtract  79                   from w-cnt-stu-pnt-stu      .
           move      w-cnt-stu-pnt-stu    to   w-cnt-stu-sav-pnt      .
           string    s-alf
