      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-rec-dea-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-rec-dea-000      thru cmp-rec-dea-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
