      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/azi/fls/ioc/obj/iofdea"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
